Name: How is shipping handled?
Answer__c: We jettison enormous blocks of raw ore to Earth to your approximate location, our AI calculates how to make it land near you (within 10 km radius), it hardly ever causes catastrophic damage.

Name: Can we purchase refined materials?
Answer__c: Mineral refining is not currently offered by Asteria; we're working on a line of drones that will refine ores with high-powered lasers, but they keep murdering their handlers.

Name: Is clone labor ethical?
Answer__c: Our clones are organic, non-GMO, and 100% vegan. Here at Asteria, the ethicality is not a concern since free will is never programmed into the clones.

Name: How long does it usually take for my order to arrive?
Answer__c: There are many factors that can influence when your order arrives at your location. Depending on how far an assigned clone has to fly for the specific ore requested, along with how abundantly available the ore is in each asteroid, it usually takes 5 to 10 business days for you order to arrive.

Name: Are there other shipping options?
Answer__c: Currently, we offer only one shipping option: jettison the enormous blocks of ore to your approximate location on earth.

Name: Where are you located?
Answer__c: Our headquarters are location on planet Globulon, in Sector 8C in the Milky Way galaxy. However, our clones can be found everywhere throughout the galaxy mining asteroids.

Name: Can I make changes to an order I already placed?
Answer__c: For the most part, no. Once an order is placed, clones are immediately assigned to the order and start searching for asteroids with the appropriate ore. However, order cancellations done before any clones are assigned will go through with no charge. If you have any issues with the ore you get, please do not hesitate to reach out to us.

Name: My order never arrived. What should I do?
Answer__c: You should first submit a ticket to see the status of your order. The clones may occasionally turn defective (and sometimes rogue) so some of the ore in your order could be taking a long time to arrive. Do not worry though, one way or another we will make sure you get your order to your approximate location.
